thread.title: Cecilia Jones

author: Cecilia Jones
title: Cecilia Jones
text:
From the moment you enter the Servcorp floor, the level of quality customer service is very evident. The ladies at reception always work diligently to assist us in identifying resolutions to our enquires, in a timely manner.
In particular Tahlea Oram, who with a very welcoming and professional personality, always goes above and beyond to assist our team. She is an outstanding asset to the Servcorp team.
